Explore, learn, have fun! Try the challenge course, archery or canoeing. Choose your adventure from these and more! The day is yours to try something new or perfect a skill you already know! Come with your troop or explore something that interests just you!

Selecting this session registers you for a half day of Archery & half day of Challenge Course for Juniors, Cadettes, Seniors and Ambasadors

All registrants must be registered Girl Scouts for the 2016 Membership Year. All adults attending this session must be registered and approved volunteers for the 2016 Membership Year. 

The last day to register for this session online or cancel and receive a refund is Sept. 21, 2015

**We are not able to accommodate tag-a-longs during this session
